# Global Agent Skills

Skills are available at ~/.local/share/agent-skills

## Available Skills

- **Jira**: Issue tracking - read ~/.local/share/agent-skills/skills/jira/SKILL.md

## Running Scripts

```bash
python skills/jira/scripts/search.py "project = DEMO"
```

## Skill Invocation

Describe naturally:
- "Search Jira for my open issues"
- "Create a bug in PROJECT about login failures"
